I"5<p>This overwhelming <a href="https://ed.ted.com/lessons?content_type=animations&amp;direction=desc&amp;sort=publish-date" target="_blank">collection</a>—in both quality and quantity—of short animated videos are intended to enhance teachers’ curriculums, but have also transformed my rainy day elliptical machine workouts from sweaty and boring (a.k.a. non-existent usually) to educational and awe-inspiring. They even have <a href="https://ed.ted.com/series/animation-basics" target="_blank">tutorials</a> about the animation used in some of the videos.</p>
